_sText:
While only discovered a year ago, the underground temple of Bhorr has caused tremendous controversy.  Various artifacts have disproven the continuity of many religious stories.  Now religious extremesits have snuck into the base of the temple and plan to collapse it before any more artifacts are recovered.

Terrorists: Destroy the temple by crumbling the entrance, or destroying the centre of its supports.

Counter-Terrorists: Save the temple and neutralize the terrorist force.
